### NRE MCP Server API Requests
# Copy-paste ready HTTP requests for testing MCP server

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888

### ===== HEALTH & STATUS =====

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get All Agents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agents

### Get State Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/state-summary

### ===== TASKS =====

### Get Task Status for Agent 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/task-status?agent=1

### Get Task Progress (Overall)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/task-progress

### Agent Claims Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/claim-task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": 1,
  "task": "Fix catalog API slug/ID handling"
}

### Agent Complete Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/task-done
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": 1,
  "task": "Fix catalog API slug/ID handling",
  "notes": "Done, tested with curl, ready for A2 to consume"
}

### ===== DEPENDENCIES =====

### Get Full Dependency Graph
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dependencies

### Get Dependencies for Agent 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dependencies?agent=1

### Get Dependencies for Agent 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dependencies?agent=2

### Get Dependencies for Agent 6
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dependencies?agent=6

### ===== BLOCKERS =====

### Get All Blockers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blockers

### Get Critical Blockers Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blockers?severity=critical

### Report Blocker
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/blockers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": 2,
  "title": "Frontend blocked waiting for API",
  "description": "Need GET /api/v1/public/catalog endpoint from Agent 1",
  "blocked_by": 1
}

### ===== COMMUNICATION =====

### Broadcast Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": 1,
  "to": "all",
  "message": "Backend API ready for consumption. Endpoint: GET /api/v1/public/catalog"
}

### Get Communication History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comms

### Get Last 20 Communications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comms?limit=20

### ===== STATE =====

### Get Full MCP State
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/state

### Get State Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/state-summary

### ===== BATCH OPERATIONS =====

### Check System Health (All Tests)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agents

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/task-progress

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/state-summary

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blockers
